\newline 

\begin_inset Formula $H_{\Omega}(\mathbf{x},\mathbf{y})=g(\nabla_{\mathbf{x}}\mathbf{w},\mathbf{y})=b\left(1-2\Phi\right)g(\nabla_{\mathbf{x}}\partial_{t},\mathbf{y})+g(\partial_{t},\mathbf{y})\nabla_{\mathbf{x}}b\left(1-2\Phi\right)$
